<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ʿjyj ʿdl ạllh qd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿajīju ʿad̊li ạllhi qad̊
 ạảs̊katãhu ại̹lay̱ ạlạảbad̊
 lamãạ ṭamat̊ lujajuhu
 ʿalaẙka yā niʿ̊ma ạlsãnad̊

[V2]
 2- ạảm̊wājuhu hadãạ̊̉tahā
 ại̹lay̱ ạltãmāmi yā ḥabīb̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ kun̊ta ʿanãạ nāyỉbaⁿạ
 bimaẘtika ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊

[V3]
 3- mā kun̊ta ạản̊ta ạl̊mudẖ̊niba
 bal̊ kunãạ naḥ̊nu ạl̊mudẖ̊nibīn̊
 lakin̊ taḥamãl̊ta ạl̊qiṣāṣ̊
 ʿani ạl̊kẖuṭāẗi ạlậtẖimīn̊

[V4]
 4- yā ʿajabaⁿạ min̊ ḥik̊maẗiⁿ
 tanawãʿat̊ fīka badat̊
 wafãẙta ḥaqã ạl̊ʿad̊li,
 wālnĩʿ̊maẗu lanā ạủẓ̊hirat̊

[V5]
 5- lạa sẖaẙʾa min̊ daẙnūnaẗiⁿ
 ại̹dẖaⁿạ ʿalay̱ ạlãdẖīna fīk̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ kulũ daẙnūnatinā
 qad̊ waqaʿat̊ fiʿ̊lạaⁿ ʿalaẙk̊

[V6]
 6- fālsẖũk̊ra nuh̊dīka ʿalay̱
 ḥubĩka naḥ̊wa ạl̊mudẖ̊nibīn̊
 wālsũb̊ḥa wāl̊ḥam̊da ại̹lay̱
 ạldãh̊ri wadah̊ri ạldãạhirīn̊</lyrics>
</song>